D8wyNMdt9NvPB7fOu-uUjg
Love, love, love this place. Our cheese monger, France, was a delightful woman who was exceptionally helpful and guided us through a huge selection of cheeses. She was generous with samples and had an instinct about what we would like. I think we ended up buying all but two of her recommendations. She was also very thoughtful in packing the cheeses for travel to the US, which was also helpful for clearing customs. I will definitely return.

